### ============================================================
### SANSKRITI DASHBOARD — Day 1 API Tests
### How to use:
###   1. Install "REST Client" extension in VS Code (humao.rest-client)
###   2. Open this file in VS Code
###   3. Click "Send Request" above any request to run it
###   4. Response appears in a split panel on the right
### ============================================================

