### DAY 6 TESTS — Wallet System
### ====================================================

### ─── Test W1: Get Wallet Balance ────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallet/balance
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── Test W2: Credit Wallet ─────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/credit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 500,
  "description": "Added money to wallet",
  "category": "TOPUP"
}


### ─── Test W3: Credit Again ──────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/credit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 1000,
  "description": "Top up for orders",
  "category": "TOPUP"
}


### ─── Test W4: Debit Wallet ──────────────────────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/debit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 200,
  "description": "Order payment #001",
  "category": "ORDER_PAYMENT"
}


### ─── Test W5: Try Debit More Than Balance ───────────
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/debit
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "amount": 99999,
  "description": "This should fail",
  "category": "OTHER"
}


### ─── Test W6: Get Transactions ──────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallet/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── Test W7: Filter CREDIT only ───────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallet/transactions?type=CREDIT
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}


### ─── Test W8: Get Wallet Summary ────────────────────
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallet/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

